"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ryr1665702696096.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ryr1665702696096.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ryr1665702696096\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      /int\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">While copying or importing data, display a message that reports the number of records copied at an interval that is expressed as a number of occurrences. By default, the interval is 100.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ryr1665702696096__p_d149849e1_d149850e1_d149851e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/int</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">MessageInterval</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1196395e66\">\n                  \n Used With\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ryr1665702696096__d7235e22\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ryr1665702696096__d7235e24\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qcr1665702695577.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qcr1665702695577.html\" title=\"Copy one or more entity occurrences from a source database or XML file to another.\">/cpy</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ryr1665702696096__d7235e30\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ryr1665702696096__d7235e32\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xsn1665702696023.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xsn1665702696023.html\" title=\"Import an XML file containing Repository definitions exported from the Uniface Repository.\">/imp</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1196395e101\">\n                  \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ryr1665702696096__p_d149864e1_d149865e1_d149866e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">MessageInterval</var>—frequency with which a message is displayed, expressed as a number of occurrences. Default is 100.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1196395e113\">\n                  \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ryr1665702696096__p_d149870e1_d149871e1_d149872e1\">Use this switch to specify another interval.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531851\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531851\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "/int Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 14, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 /int While copying or importing data, display a message that reports the number of records copied at an interval that is expressed as a number of occurrences. By default, the interval is 100. /int = MessageInterval Used With /cpy /imp Parameters MessageInterval —frequency with which a message is displayed, expressed as a number of occurrences. Default is 100. Description Use this switch to specify another interval. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}